aima.core.environment.map

Class SimpleMapAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.agent.impl.AbstractAgent
      • aima.core.search.framework.SimpleProblemSolvingAgent
        • aima.core.environment.map.SimpleMapAgent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Agent, EnvironmentObject

    public class SimpleMapAgent
extends SimpleProblemSolvingAgent
    Note: This implementation should be used with one predefined goal only or with uninformed search. As the heuristic of the used search algorithm is never changed, estimates for the second (or randomly created goal) will be wrong.
    Author:
    Ciaran O'Reilly, Ruediger Lunde
